{"type": "article", "id": 20175, "title": "“别有洞天”，就是这 7 张图里的湛蓝冰洞世界", "description": "真的是，冰洞。", "date": "2016-01-04T12:08:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1265, "name": "冰岛"}, {"id": 21532, "name": "冰洞"}], "category": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 143, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071532298mxHJbgRopTPUaj3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">这是法国摄影师肖巴尔（Jean-Francois Chaubard）在冰岛拍下一系列的冰川照片，照片中展现出冰洞内的湛蓝世界，所有景色都仿佛像是加上了蓝色滤镜，呈现出不同深浅程度的蓝。肖巴尔表示，这次“别有洞天”的冰洞只能透过穿越冰川到达，初次进入冰洞时，洞口位置较窄，完全不能站直走路，但愈走入洞内便愈开阔，冰洞的高度约为 10 公尺，全洞长约 98 公尺，绵延不绝，让他赞叹在蓝色包围的世界下，令人感觉格外平和！肖巴尔甚至一度走到洞外，利用洞景来张自拍照，可说是特别难以忘怀的经验。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153224V72sD1wZmeNljQWL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153224iKbkgQw87TpVafA9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153225OhHYS6b2K3GlRVvp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153226dGBh9V0er1HNgQYJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153226u4XRfQOH3pFidvIP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153227iORlE3o8kB504CFG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153228vhLIlDVQG7YTWnte.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t题图来自 <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/25949441@N02/10856734986\" target=\"_blank\">flickr</a> ，文中图片来自 <span style=\"text-align:left;\">Jean Fran ois Chaubard/Solent News Photo Agency</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}